<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Date</th>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1937-07-07"><a href="/wiki/July_7" title="July 7">7 July</a> <a href="/wiki/1937" title="1937">1937</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1945-09-09"><a href="/wiki/September_9" title="September 9">9 September</a> <a href="/wiki/1945" title="1945">1945</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Location</th>
<td><span class="location"><a href="/wiki/Asia" title="Asia">Asia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Pacific_Ocean" title="Pacific Ocean">Pacific Ocean</a>, its islands and neighboring countries.</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Result</th>
<td><a href="/wiki/Allies_of_World_War_II" title="Allies of World War II">Allied</a> victory, fall of the <a href="/wiki/Empire_of_Japan" title="Empire of Japan">Empire of Japan</a></td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
