<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Casualties and losses</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;"><b>China:</b> 3.8 million soldiers killed, 17+ million civilians killed<sup class="noprint Template-Fact"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources&#160;since October 2007" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</span></sup><br />
<p><b>United Kingdom</b> 52,000 killed (12,000 in captivity):<br /></p>
<ul>
<li><b>Indian Empire</b>: 86,838 killed</li>
</ul>
<p><b>USA:</b> 106,207 killed, 248,316 wounded and missing<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
<b>Philippines</b>: 57,000 killed<br />
<b>Australia</b>: 17,501 killed<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
<b>Soviet Union</b>: 12,031 killed and missing, 24,425 wounded and sick<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup><br /></p>
</td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;">1,740,955 military deaths<br />
393,000 civilian deaths<sup class="noprint Template-Fact"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources&#160;since October 2007" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</span></sup></td>
</tr>
