<tr>
<th style=";background-color: #B0C4DE; font-size: 90%;" colspan="2" class="navbox-title">
<div style="float:left; width:6em;text-align:left;">
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;;background-color: #B0C4DE; font-size: 90%;;border:none;; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Campaignbox_Pacific_War" title="Template:Campaignbox Pacific War"><span title="View this template" style=";background-color: #B0C4DE; font-size: 90%;;border:none;">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Campaignbox_Pacific_War" title="Template talk:Campaignbox Pacific War"><span title="Discussion about this template" style=";background-color: #B0C4DE; font-size: 90%;;border:none;">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Pacific_War&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Pacific_War&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";background-color: #B0C4DE; font-size: 90%;;border:none;;">e</span></a></div>
</div>
<div style="padding: 0.2em 0; line-height: 1.3em;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong class="selflink">Pacific War</strong></span></div>
</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px;">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Second_Sino-Japanese_War" title="Second Sino-Japanese War">China</a> – <a href="/wiki/Pacific_Ocean_theater_of_World_War_II" title="Pacific Ocean theater of World War II">Pacific&#160;Ocean</a> – <a href="/wiki/South-East_Asian_theatre_of_World_War_II" title="South-East Asian theatre of World War II">South-East&#160;Asia</a> – <a href="/wiki/South_West_Pacific_theatre_of_World_War_II" title="South West Pacific theatre of World War II">South&#160;West&#160;Pacific</a> – <a href="/wiki/Japan_campaign" title="Japan campaign">Japan</a> – <a href="/wiki/Soviet_invasion_of_Manchuria_(1945)" title="Soviet invasion of Manchuria (1945)">Manchuria&#160;(1945)</a></div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>The <b>Pacific War</b> was the part of <a href="/wiki/World_War_II" title="World War II">World War II</a>—and preceding conflicts—that took place in the <a href="/wiki/Pacific_Ocean" title="Pacific Ocean">Pacific Ocean</a>, its islands, and in <a href="/wiki/East_Asia" title="East Asia">East Asia</a>, between <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1937-07-07"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="07-07"><a href="/wiki/July_7" title="July 7">July 7</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1937" title="1937">1937</a></span> and <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1945-08-14"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-14"><a href="/wiki/August_14" title="August 14">August 14</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1945" title="1945">1945</a></span>. The most decisive actions took place after the <a href="/wiki/Empire_of_Japan" title="Empire of Japan">Empire of Japan</a> attacked various countries, who together came to be known as the <a href="/wiki/Allies_of_World_War_II" title="Allies of World War II">Allies</a> (or Allied powers).</p>
