<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> The Emperor was using the Army to keep the <i>Diet</i> off-balance and shore up Imperial prestige, so he did not use his authority to rein in "cowboy generals" in China, even as the China war dragged on. Bix, <i>Hirohito</i>.</li>
